```json
{
  "application": "NAMD",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "NAMD",
      "CharmRun",
      "OpenMPI"
    ],
    "resources": [
      "PBS",
      "nodes",
      "ppn",
      "OpenIB"
    ],
    "environment_variables": [
      "NAMD_PATH",
      "LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
      "NAMD",
      "CHARMRUN",
      "PBS_O_WORKDIR",
      "PBS_NODEFILE"
    ],
    "files": [
      "nodelist",
      "mpiexec_wrapper"
    ],
    "commands": [
      "module unload openmpi",
      "rm -f nodelist",
      "touch nodelist",
      "cat $PBS_NODEFILE | awk '!seen[$0]++'",
      "echo $node >> nodelist",
      "cat $PBS_NODEFILE | wc -l",
      "cat $PBS_NODEFILE | awk '!seen[$0]++' | wc -l",
      "expr $NP - $NN",
      "($NP-$NN*2)",
      "echo \"#!/bin/csh\" > mpiexec_wrapper",
      "echo \"exec mpiexec -machinefile ./nodelist -mca btl openib,self,sm \$*\" >> mpiexec_wrapper",
      "chmod +x mpiexec_wrapper",
      "date"
    ]
  }
}
```
